description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP checks in with Tampa. Bucs Beat Writer Greg Auman shares more details about what happened with Antonio Brown. The Voice of the SEC Paul Finebaum joins the show to discuss the impression Cincy made as a group of 5 team. And Carson Palmer tells us why he wouldn't have opted out of a bowl game.
